Namespace: Celestial.UIToolkit.Media.Animations

Syntax
public abstract class AnimationUsingKeyFramesBase<T, TKeyFrame, TKeyFrameCollection> : AnimationBase<T>, ISealable, IAnimatable, DUCE.IResource, IAddChild, IKeyFrameAnimation, ISegmentLengthProvider where TKeyFrame : IInterpolateKeyFrame<T> where TKeyFrameCollection : Freezable, IList, IList<TKeyFrame>, new()
Type Parameters
Name Description
T

The type of animated object.
TKeyFrame

The type of key frame which is being used by this animation.
TKeyFrameCollection

The type of collection which holds the animation's key frames.

FreezeCore(Boolean)

Makes this animation unmodifiable or checks if it can be made unmodifiable.

Declaration
protected override bool FreezeCore(bool isChecking)
Parameters
Type Name Description
Boolean isChecking

true to return an indication of whether the object can be frozen (without actually freezing it); false to actually freeze the object.
Returns
Type Description
Boolean

If isChecking is true, this method returns true if the Freezable can be made unmodifiable, or false if it cannot be made unmodifiable.

If isChecking is false, this method returns true if the specified Freezable is now unmodifiable, or false if it cannot be made unmodifiable.
